,\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"memory_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend服务\",\n      \"reason\": \"多个frontend实例的error_ratio、server_error_ratio和rrt指标显著异常，响应时间从正常11.6秒激增至900万秒以上\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: error_ratio从0%升至21.06%，rrt从11658.51ms升至9056952.96ms；frontend-1: error_ratio从0%升至21.43%，rrt从11661.64ms升至9104613.86ms；frontend-2: error_ratio从0%升至20.58%，rrt从11700.79ms升至7585958.9ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"shippingservice多个实例的error_ratio和client_error_ratio异常，错误率高达60-63%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-0: error_ratio p99从0%升至60%；shippingservice-1: error_ratio p99从0%升至63.16%；shippingservice-2: error_ratio p99从0%升至63.16%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\", \n      \"reason\": \"productcatalogservice实例的error_ratio和client_error_ratio异常，错误率超过40%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-0: error_ratio从0%升至44.44%；productcatalogservice-2: error_ratio从0%升至42.86%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice多个实例的error_ratio和client_error_ratio异常，p99错误率高达46-48%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-0: error_ratio p99从0%升至48%；cartservice-1: error_ratio p99从0%升至48%；cartservice-2: error_ratio p99从0%升至46.15%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"redis-cart-0的pod_cpu_usage异常，p99值从0.08降至0.0，可能表示服务不可用\",\n      \"evidence\": \"redis-cart-0: pod_cpu_usage p99从0.08降至0.0，pod_cpu_usage中位数从0.0降至0.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-pd\",\n      \"reason\": \"tidb-pd的memory_usage异常，p99内存使用量显著下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"tidb-pd: memory_usage p99从192417792.0降至153530368.0，下降比例22.48%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结：**\n\n1. **服务级异常广泛存在**：多个核心服务（frontend、shippingservice、productcatalogservice、cartservice）都出现了严重的错误率异常和响应时间激增。\n\n2. **关键发现**：frontend服务的响